{"tid":440913,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【綠置居】六旬婦為供樓延退休：有得揀我唔會再買","createTime":"2017-10-19T08:08:38.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-19T12:59:56.000Z","uid":75969,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":36,"replies":[{"pid":"724224bffd452948b4a18680859820bfde336bd7","tid":440913,"uid":75969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:08:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20171017/large/1508245783_241e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20171017%2Flarge%2F1508245783_241e.jpg&h=92160ae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">王先生由公屋仔搖身一變做業主，每月住屋開支大增，即使要孭起20幾年房債，也甘願一世做樓奴。馬泉祟攝<br />\n</span><br />\n首個綠置居項目新蒲崗景泰苑今年初推售時，吸引大批綠表公屋戶申請，最終超額認購18倍。有景泰苑業主為一圓置業夢，即使要孭起20多年房債，也甘願一世做樓奴；有業主原本計劃退休，但為了供樓，「依家幾十歲人都要返工，為咗供樓有乜辦法。」直言若可再選擇，「有得揀我唔會再買（綠置居）」。<br />\n<br />\n陳太一家三口以綠表購買景泰苑低層一個兩房大單位，樓價約270萬元。其單位面向啟德發展區及太子道東，售價較其他單位相對貴。她入住後指理想與現實相差很大，「環境好差，交通唔方便，好嘈，全部窗要閂哂先瞓到，就算有隔音窗都幫唔到乜野。」她說交還公屋單位時，「房署要還原（間屋），使咗幾萬蚊，呢到又要10幾萬裝修，失哂預算」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>年約60歲的她，未做業主前原本計劃退休，「依家幾十歲人都要返工，為咗供樓有乜辦法。」直言若可從頭選擇，「有得揀我唔會再買（綠置居）」。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n另一業主王先生一家三口，早前以綠表申請景泰苑，最終以約208萬購入低層一個約393平方呎一房單位。他早前已支付約11萬元首期，向銀行借足95%按揭，供款期25年，現時每月供款約9,000元。<br />\n<br />\n單位正裝修，最快月底可入伙。王先生由公屋仔搖身一變做業主，每月住屋開支大增，「以前住公屋每個月都係畀約1,900蚊租，仲要係老豆畀，但依家淨係供樓，同老豆兩個人夾埋最少要畀9,000蚊，仲未計管理費、差餉」。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>王先生孭起25年按揭，坦言感到壓力，「由無負擔變咗有負擔，10年後（老豆退休）甚至變咗全部我自己孭起哂，未來幾廿年都絕對唔可以失業。」但他直言為圓置業夢甘願做「樓奴」，「為退休而作準備，好擔心退休後要再交租。」</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n政府加推火炭4,800個綠置居單位，社會有意見斥政府用公帑資助基層人士置業，王先生承認自己獲雙重福利，「無可否認我係雙重受惠者，住咗咁耐公屋，仲有機會買樓」。他認為政府應在有足夠公屋建屋量，才加推綠置居，「相信到時會無咁多人眼紅」。  <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57340697\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57340697&d=awM1WCYJ6JNa6LRpoiqvWp4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=ba33eb1f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fnews%2F20171018%2F57340697&h=f7f628f6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/news/20171018/57340697</a>"},{"pid":"6c444ef76814f5a53cb87f4ac716e8305bdf7332","tid":440913,"uid":75969,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:09:07.000Z","msg":"做死一世<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b171715c6f0ffb7068d3fdd1741f3bbaf0ed8dda","tid":440913,"uid":22566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:09:42.000Z","msg":"Ok"},{"pid":"57ec8fa1e3c39cae46afce120574cd859289eb38","tid":440913,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:10:12.000Z","msg":"冇樓退休點交租"},{"pid":"7b3c7323277e7c5d378c50f168e77969ea8504d0","tid":440913,"uid":53223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:10:13.000Z","msg":"政府真係好衰，榨乾你為止<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2d8e0c496181f8c0213212af2ef2f38365dce3","tid":440913,"uid":130513,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:16:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3df44814a207ebfbcce91503c07e1be3cc4854cd","tid":440913,"uid":52276,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:17:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇樓退休點交租</blockquote><br />\n退休冇錢咪拎綜援囉"},{"pid":"973d645094438e05a1cb40af564439e4822fbb5e","tid":440913,"uid":1482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:18:23.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">有得揀</span></span>"},{"pid":"5de14bc97912053b0674ba8926b48911dad8d058","tid":440913,"uid":117200,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:20:58.000Z","msg":"你估你退休就唔洗再比錢咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n淨係管理費每個月千五蚊 每廿五年做一次大廈維修都玩死你啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4451af92b1dc2eadf62400fa850d2314c353a1b9","tid":440913,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:24:05.000Z","msg":"60歲有公屋住到死仲買咩樓"},{"pid":"9db22c43654202d471bcdc0cf9c71695fb75a8fd","tid":440913,"uid":15647,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>60歲有公屋住到死仲買咩樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係弱X 智<br />\n景泰苑都算好住啦，入彩虹邨就有地鐵站，一出去有個巴士總站，呢邊都唔方便，香港無地方叫交通方便 wo"},{"pid":"b05c7232dc66b9981f63685f97e87e9487109451","tid":440913,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:30:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4b7d841e063cda2b44f48e08b30ce8350cfab2c3","tid":440913,"uid":55533,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:31:57.000Z","msg":"為左間垃圾唔要公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n時代唔同啦<br />\n而歸住公屋好過住私樓"},{"pid":"e1fbcf6fa58d1aa998b9241a338a6601685e1220","tid":440913,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:34:32.000Z","msg":"Oct 17近期活躍五毛<br />\n1三色貓<br />\n2群龍共舞<br />\n3法國佬巫斯義=香港鍵國<br />\n4真律師何君堯<br />\n5newlife<br />\n6侵B<br />\n7返六日唔撚易<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">8dewi</span></span><br />\n9bb chu<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">10優美開始</span></span>"},{"pid":"7c311ba7b936ee45b94f7d4d26965f3ba5a0d3b5","tid":440913,"uid":19712,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:36:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>60歲有公屋住到死仲買咩樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係弱X 智<br />\n景泰苑都算好住啦，入彩虹邨就有地鐵站，一出去有個巴士總站，呢邊都唔方便，香港無地方叫交通方便 wo</blockquote><br />\n個位兩頭唔到岸 起鑽石山同彩虹中間<br />\n無錯有巴士站 但個距離點都唔夠上面鳳德方便<br />\n為左一手樓可以去到幾盡 隔離就馬路 附近又多車房 成日D響喉嘈到PK"},{"pid":"82393c20af4cab483ccc15ac905ac4df9d44de1c","tid":440913,"uid":15647,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:42:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>60歲有公屋住到死仲買咩樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係弱X 智<br />\n景泰苑都算好住啦，入彩虹邨就有地鐵站，一出去有個巴士總站，呢邊都唔方便，香港無地方叫交通方便 wo</blockquote><br />\n個位兩頭唔到岸 起鑽石山同彩虹中間<br />\n無錯有巴士站 但個距離點都唔夠上面鳳德方便<br />\n為左一手樓可以去到幾盡 隔離就馬路 附近又多車房 成日D響喉嘈到PK</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行去兩個地鐵站都係兩個字度<br />\n巴士站行過去最多咪一個字，呢個距離真係唔可以講唔方便<br />\n你講隔離係馬路，彩虹邨面對啟德咪又係同一條路，唔覺有幾嘈"},{"pid":"2a5e37fdd34c774e9d88329433dfd03effc8242b","tid":440913,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:42:19.000Z","msg":"黎緊仲有個彩興苑 <br />\n話就話彩虹 但上到去彩雲咁遠<br />\n遲早實有班買家話上落條斜路好唔方便之類 <br />\n之後又會話配套唔夠好<br />\n梅窩唔洗講喇 買完無唔想入去住 除非渡假喇"},{"pid":"08952fb53289010ff646b9b8ab6e7cae4a63ddf9","tid":440913,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:51:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>60歲有公屋住到死仲買咩樓</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咪就係弱X 智<br />\n景泰苑都算好住啦，入彩虹邨就有地鐵站，一出去有個巴士總站，呢邊都唔方便，香港無地方叫交通方便 wo</blockquote><br />\n個位兩頭唔到岸 起鑽石山同彩虹中間<br />\n無錯有巴士站 但個距離點都唔夠上面鳳德方便<br />\n為左一手樓可以去到幾盡 隔離就馬路 附近又多車房 成日D響喉嘈到PK</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你行去兩個地鐵站都係兩個字度<br />\n巴士站行過去最多咪一個字，呢個距離真係唔可以講唔方便<br />\n你講隔離係馬路，彩虹邨面對啟德咪又係同一條路，唔覺有幾嘈</blockquote><br />\n遲D擴建埋鑽石山站就一定鑽石山站近 行去彩虹站就真係唔好講笑喇<br />\n搭巴士想多車要行去越秀 一係上返龍翔道<br />\n或者你試下果個位落車感受下個噪音你會明白"},{"pid":"05d5a45ebe9be7142f78c3e095711e36d5d7eb4b","tid":440913,"uid":6211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:55:41.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: blue;\">向銀行借足95%按揭，供款期25年</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n買間垃圾公屋都要比銀行賺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"09ccafe1ccca3ec70d0c51e686d96e3386a2f3db","tid":440913,"uid":95,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T08:56:06.000Z","msg":"60歲人唔死都大半世，有間公屋個個月交千零蚊租走去買樓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你交二千蚊租，一年都係二萬四，當你有九十歲命要交三十年租都係720,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e09860535bc49aa9121775e2c3240826f54ed4d","tid":440913,"uid":113000,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:04:16.000Z","msg":"地圖咩位要關哂窗先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2247ff79b11322d2b300fb165d0dad264410c436","tid":440913,"uid":19712,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:07:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>地圖咩位要關哂窗先訓到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n對著條太子道東個方向"},{"pid":"eff1ea6b960bccbf950ccd40c532a50b2d4cff2a","tid":440913,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>60歲人唔死都大半世，有間公屋個個月交千零蚊租走去買樓。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當你交二千蚊租，一年都係二萬四，當你有九十歲命要交三十年租都係720,000<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n高齡工作<br />\n隨時捱到命都短幾年<br />\n可能七十幾歲就病死"},{"pid":"09378cc6d72b0c8e3c328cc9b8227e7ac3f4f3b4","tid":440913,"uid":7371,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:20:27.000Z","msg":"個後生仔話供樓為左退休唔駛交租<br />\n但你公屋住到老可能只係交百幾萬租<br />\n到你住公屋老左又會多D褔利可減租<br />\n<br />\n上樓除左供幾廿年<br />\n每個月仲要比好貴管理費<br />\n貴管理費變相其實係一種租<br />\n只係個價目名改個令你易D接受嘅名<br />\n<br />\n其實應該係計幾十年總開支<br />\n唔好貪老左唔駛交租<br />\n上完樓但老左仲要交貴管理費都好甘<br />\n<br />\n等佢老豆退休埋<br />\n佢就會知有幾大壓力<br />\n中年失業或轉工都驚死"},{"pid":"3abdce254750176abc3073577682726965101ed1","tid":440913,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-19T09:21:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>供25年 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n野原廣志"}]}